  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      58.46,
      311.86,
      566.0,
      344.37
    ],
    "text": "Four Suspects Arrested for Illegally Storing and Possessing Diesel \u2013 Kelaniya Divisional Criminal Investigation Bureau",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      58.46,
      356.78,
      565.67,
      422.51
    ],
    "text": "Based on information received by the Senior Superintendent of Police in charge of the Kelaniya Division, a team of officers attached to the Kelaniya Divisional Criminal Investigation Bureau conducted a raid on the evening of 11.03.2026 in the Pahala Biyagama area of the Biyagama Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      58.46,
      434.68,
      565.59,
      466.43
    ],
    "text": "During the operation, four suspects were arrested along with two bowsers containing 19,060 (nineteen thousand and sixty) litres of diesel that had been illegally stored.",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      58.46,
      478.72,
      565.86,
      510.35
    ],
    "text": "The arrested suspects, along with the seized diesel bowsers, were handed over to the Biyagama Police Station for further legal action.",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      58.46,
      522.64,
      565.79,
      588.26
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the suspects had allegedly paid money to drivers of vehicles such as lorries, tippers, and prime movers operating on the roads without proper authorization, and had extracted diesel from the fuel tanks of those vehicles. The fuel had then been stored in specially prepared tanks and later sold for profit.",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      58.46,
      600.55,
      565.42,
      649.22
    ],
    "text": "During the raid, police officers also seized two motorized pumps used for extracting fuel from vehicles, sixteen iron barrels, and cash amounting to Rs. 381,000/- (three hundred and eighty-one thousand).",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      58.46,
      661.51,
      565.56,
      693.14
    ],
    "text": "The suspects, aged 20, 22, 32, and 42 years, are residents of the Heiyanthuduwa, Thihagoda, and Nelumdeniya areas.",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      58.46,
      705.43,
      565.47,
      737.06
    ],
    "text": "The suspects are scheduled to be produced before the Mahara Magistrate\u2019s Court on 12.03.2026, while further investigations are being carried out by the Biyagama Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "IskoolaPota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
